objective:
使學生熟悉燃料電池之種類、特性、原理等相關知識。訓練學生具備運用氫能之潔淨能源，來取代具污染性能源的能力，培養學生善用潔淨能源與環境保護之態度與觀念，實際瞭解燃料電池系統之運作。授課內容為：燃料電池系統簡介、效率與開路電流電壓、質子交換膜燃料電池、固態氧化物燃料電池、電化學反應熱力學、燃料電池類別、專題報告與實驗。
This course introduces the types, characteristics and principles of fuel cell. Demonstrate an understanding of the hydrogen economy and zero-emission energy. The course also performs the detail of operation procedure of the whole fuel cell system. The course outline includes: 
1.　　Introduction to the fuel cell system;
2.　　System operating efficiency &amp; open circuit I-V response;
3.　　PEM FC;
4.　　SOFC;
5.　　Thermodynamics of electrochemistry;
6.　　Introduction to the types of fuel cell;
7.　　Report &amp; experiment.
